# /doctrina-why — provenance for {{PROJECT_NAME}}

Explain why a capability exists and is shaped as it is.

Run `doctrina why <capability>` and relay the provenance chain it prints: the
product intent it Realizes, its purpose and status, the acceptance criteria
that prove it (with cited evidence), the accepted ADRs that decided it, and
the archived changes that built it. Read-only — answer from the artifacts,
don't grep the tree by hand.
